{"tid":12713,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[公審] [虐畜]係唔去睇獸醫呀，你吹得我脹？","createTime":"2016-11-29T18:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T02:23:35.000Z","uid":5701,"like":70,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2a2a2ea75c089b62641914dc1232e679f86b44","tid":12713,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"今日喺fb個寵物group到見到個post話有個主人隻天竺鼠有唇炎啦，唔知各位巴絲知唔知咩係天竺鼠呢，拿以下係當時人既照片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/020659_4f4e87617740e96f7a27daed35312450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F020659_4f4e87617740e96f7a27daed35312450.jpg&h=f9212b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好得意呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過呢有養開寵物既都知道，唔只人會病，寵物都會有病，而且醫藥費仲好貴添，而好不幸地其中一隻鼠就有唇炎，嚴重既仲會導致口腔潰爛，無法進食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8CN4EFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8CN4EFt.jpg&h=7196664c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想信各位巴絲作為一個好既主人遇到衣啲情況既話，應該會好不猶豫咁帶自己心愛既寵物去睇獸醫啦，而當時人既主人就選擇放上group問下意見既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過問題黎啦，事關當時人既主人好想成為傑青而努力儲首期啦，雖然group裏面大家都一致叫佢快啲去睇醫生，嚴重起上黎真係可大可小，不過佢就堅決唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/022502_473837689f7acd48d29b51bb3d05578a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F022502_473837689f7acd48d29b51bb3d05578a.jpg&h=777f15f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到啲咁既回應係人到火滾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以大家都話佢，最後男主角見到自己條女比人話就出黎爆seed啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/023219_39131d1dd2e79365db2fbc5c33ee9007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F023219_39131d1dd2e79365db2fbc5c33ee9007.jpg&h=149e88c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係LIHKG既一眾巴絲點睇呢，以前喺高登果陣大家都好有愛心，唔知過左黎既大家仲有冇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隨帖附上男女主角圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/024056_e904e79bda21e275b3cddbe7f211824d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F024056_e904e79bda21e275b3cddbe7f211824d.jpg&h=0c3f5f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/024109_198e53102eaa6396fb42ca0f457aaef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F024109_198e53102eaa6396fb42ca0f457aaef7.jpg&h=70df070f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：冇錢就咪學人養死返大陸啦大陸哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊追擊兩條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：隻野人地養死唔死既關你鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持佢地腥鹼人儲錢買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898f68d1ca430d718b66531219ee1b46f3c42d2f","tid":12713,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:50:38.000Z","msg":"LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ae7d1247ae18605eb0c263a13d8fa885693d76","tid":12713,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:53:29.000Z","msg":"唔好咩都放上黎啦"},{"pid":"896fbb161c4599843efb5c493fd155198de88680","tid":12713,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你幾點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b227bbd307a83ad8b8e04c242264d839c182aab3","tid":12713,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"你當高登係咩？處刑場？"},{"pid":"c9b7b8692bf66e2fcd1f6181f561361b249913f2","tid":12713,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身都想覆，<br />\n你加左呢句我真係唔想再講咩"},{"pid":"9a1838708c8bf3af66f506c6e3451a1f850a2afa","tid":12713,"uid":3253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"d8a3f7b138062a51d6ce88dbeb6e6f747ce3c651","tid":12713,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd28d22b042625da54f942c3e2ac5ea636c688c","tid":12713,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你想我地點姐 佢係咁厚願無恥可以點 唔通我地屌兩屌佢就肯帶寵物睇醫生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542eb8e2646222a71d45464cb224da0c04ecde4f","tid":12713,"uid":37289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:18:13.000Z","msg":"咁又要公審呀？隻動物係屬於佢傢喎 關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1476b69878096ad64937316faa4923ee62cc8226","tid":12713,"uid":9748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9</blockquote><br />\n十足十啲道德塔利班唔推就mark你冇愛心<br />\n見到依種人就好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91298a4309225a018c7f450eb7429900bbc9e3c6","tid":12713,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;LIHKG原來冇人有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOn9&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n十足十啲道德塔利班唔推就mark你冇愛心<br />\n見到依種人就好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，仲要開完post先2分鐘嘈喧巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ad7186050971b30c5a7b6400fcf0bc9ae755a7","tid":12713,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:15:30.000Z","msg":"芝麻綠豆都要放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c3bad7e32170d6b88d31b0c5ffffbd6d9a997e","tid":12713,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:20:02.000Z","msg":"駛唔撚駛我今朝踩親棵草都比你拎出嚟審呀？"},{"pid":"ab15a136f78d204427c46b6b917f62390757864c","tid":12713,"uid":13047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"對件事: 死大陸喱做錯野仲發茅<br />\n<br />\n對樓主: on9少陣啦"},{"pid":"4feba9777bad075e888f952ac401dd83982d0c98","tid":12713,"uid":13479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:34:03.000Z","msg":"道德塔利班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a0b0681ad6b841083b6525f4f130bb2acffe6b","tid":12713,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a79b350b31388a1653059d1c3b5eebe7ca929f","tid":12713,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"點解你地要係咁屌樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明個對男女真係好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f943c4c16083310b606aadc6d454d54fd9c972","tid":12713,"uid":36815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"冇人推就自己推啦硬膠樓主<br />\n條女係有錯<br />\n但你個態度似係想博人認同你多過屌柒對男女多d囉"},{"pid":"c7285ce30fd8ae0116cb7af15c62855ced0525cf","tid":12713,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"唔願放錢落寵物到 不如唔好養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114f80e1e36ca4e2df5573d0e52eab1432499f31","tid":12713,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"on9無腦大陸